TY  - JOUR
TI  - Optimal Paths of Capital Accumulation Under the Minimum Time Objective
AU  - Kurz, Mordecai
AB  - [The properties of the optimal growth path are investigated in a two-sector economy model. The objective is the attainment of the von Neumann path in minimum time, and the optimal strategy is given. In order to characterize and establish the optimality of the path, an extensive use is made of Pontrayagin's Maximum Principle.]
C1  - Full publication date: Jan., 1965
DB  - JSTOR
DO  - 10.2307/1911888
EP  - 66
