TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Information Approach to Demand Analysis
AU  - Theil, H.
AB  - [This article approaches demand analysis in a probabilistic manner. The main ingredient is the value share (the proportion of total expenditure spent on a particular commodity), which can be regarded as a probability in view of the fact that it is nonnegative and adds up to one when summed over all commodities.This ingredient is used for the formulation of price and quantity index numbers and demand equations, partly in the light of information theory.]
C1  - Full publication date: Jan., 1965
DB  - JSTOR
DO  - 10.2307/1911889
EP  - 87
IS  - 1
PB  - [Wiley, Econometric Society]
